{"tid":1108640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IBM AI 系統預測員工何時想「劈炮」，準確率高達 95%！","createTime":"2019-04-16T05:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T10:33:23.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fbed5d937c91e3c125969c3a3cddede86c0dc5a5","tid":1108640,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"隨著 AI 人工智能不斷發展， 各間大公司都紛紛以人工智能取代原有的人類員工，以節省開支及提高生產力。如今， IBM 在超級電腦 Watson 上開發出一套系統，可以預測員工何時打算離職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，讓公司及時挽留優秀員工，準確率更高達 95% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/ibm-world-headquarters-c-zahner-6058-1200x675.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fibm-world-headquarters-c-zahner-6058-1200x675.jpg&h=85de292e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n據 IBM CEO Ginni Rometty 表示，有關系統會在評估多方面資料後，及時找出即將產生離職想法的員工，讓公司可以及時採取挽留措施，避免優秀的員工離職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而 Rometty 亦指有關系統只是 IBM 改革的一部分，更指出未來 AI V將會更加有效地協助人類工作。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/04/10/ibm-ai/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F10%2Fibm-ai%2Flife-tech%2F&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=9cfd0910\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/04/10/ibm-ai/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"db65452a12f11a5945c021ce0f8d6bbe6dcaa146","tid":1108640,"uid":201992,"like":2,"dislike":67,"score":-65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，<br />\n請勿負評干擾運作。"},{"pid":"5f4a4c5ba05bed61cec5d4d1b99e4991ec35f2e5","tid":1108640,"uid":1886,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"事實上，透過雲端運算及先進 AI ， IBM 已將人力資源部門的員工總數減少 30% ，讓員工享有更高薪金及完成更具價值的工作。 Rometty 亦預期， AI 將於未來 5 至 10 年內大幅衝擊所有職業，而 AI 較擅長的工作亦會交予它們，同時只有真正的人才可保住工作。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/11181931/28776001667_6dba25bb3c_k-e1549880391342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F11181931%2F28776001667_6dba25bb3c_k-e1549880391342.jpg&h=a92b998b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/04/09/ibm-use-ai-to-prediction-resign-for-employee/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F04%2F09%2Fibm-use-ai-to-prediction-resign-for-employee%2F&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdx1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=05e28387\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/04/09/ibm-use-ai-to-prediction-resign-for-employee/</a>"},{"pid":"602f273d383cd4bae7d078a3a8c1e6054cbf8340","tid":1108640,"uid":64009,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:42:32.000Z","msg":"香港老細: 走左仲有千千萬萬個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cfa75d80f59ae6146ea56648d3bc67b9991202","tid":1108640,"uid":48679,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"if accessToJobsdb == true<br />\nthen intendToLeave = true"},{"pid":"ec9cb3312bf9a97a58bbc9f861eedde9e6a2c8f3","tid":1108640,"uid":20241,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"IBM 已將人力資源部門的員工總數減少 30%"},{"pid":"3b2e3a59e6a88c72e6726bf75078ed7b29024c09","tid":1108640,"uid":3465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T05:58:21.000Z","msg":"濕鳩hr仲有乜撚野用呀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a067a48605348c40d85bc62d4b86fad251d922b","tid":1108640,"uid":48234,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:21:13.000Z","msg":"同時<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有真正的人</sp